description:
What do you guys think about this pandemic? Personally I do not know how I feel about this image just yet, though many loopholes are starting to show up. The seasonal flu kills more Americans than this virus. Why must we lockdown every single state, even shen certain states like Wyoming, Maine, New Mexico, Nebraska and Alaska, etc. have less than 500 cases? Why are we destined for 'essential' items? Is social distancing really going to help? Why are there curfews for the virus when many people still have to return home from work & see family? It all is overwhelming. There must be many unknown unknowns. Just looking to have a discussion about all of these things mentioned in this photo. #Repost @righthandpath 
Artist: @grrrgraphics
